title: PORTISHEAD --PEARL-- 1999
description:
Portishead / Mandalay - Pearl 
 Label: Go! Beat  
Catalog#: 777 115-3  
Format: CD, Unofficial Release
 
Country: UK 
Released: 2000 
Genre: Electronic  
Style: Trip Hop  
Notes: An infamous bootleg, this album
 is actually a repackaging of Mandalay&#039;s
 &#039;Empathy&#039; album, expertly repackaged
 and credited to Portishead.
 Even the production and songwriting
 credits are attributed to Geoff Barrow
 and Beth Gibbons, though the credits
 belong to Mandalay. The track &#039;Opposites&#039;
 from Empathy has been renamed &#039;Pearl&#039; here.
